0.1.0
=====
- Initial version, tested with Fedora Core 7 (Test 3)

0.1.1
=====
- Updated version, tested with Xubuntu Feisty (Beta)

0.1.2
=====
- Minor changes, to icon drawing and path settings

0.2.0
=====
- Panel plugin renamed, to "xfce4-smartpm-plugin"
- Support added for Yum+Extender and APT+Synaptic

0.2.1
=====
- Minor packaging changes, tested with F-8 / Gutsy
- Fixed some bugs with wrong icon and apt warnings

0.2.2
=====
- Minor changes, added flag for upgrade/dist-upgrade

0.3.0
=====
- Optionally showing notifications for new upgrades
- Support added for slapt/gslapt (Slackware/Vector)

0.3.1
=====
- Bugfix for Xubuntu package, was not finding gksudo

0.3.2
=====
- Minor changes, added flag for "su" vs. "sudo" auth
- Fixed bug looking in old path only for "smart-root"
